@startuml
title Backup and Recovery Flow
participant BackupPolicy
participant BackupStore
participant RecoveryTeam
participant PlatformState

BackupPolicy -> BackupStore: schedule backup
BackupStore -> PlatformState: capture snapshot
RecoveryTeam -> BackupStore: request restore
BackupStore -> PlatformState: restore state
PlatformState --> RecoveryTeam: recovery confirmed
@enduml
